snippet.title: Wurroom Trailer
snippet.description:
Wurroom is an interactive art experience, disguised as an exploration adventure game, relieved through the story of a Hand, lost in unknown worlds and unclaimed realities.

Release of the game is scheduled for autumn 2019 - and the game will be free! 
Wishlist so you don't miss it: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1153130/Wurroom/
